{
  "name": "Village",
  "scenes": [
    {
      "id": "village_forest_entrance",
      "name": "Village - Entrance",
      "paragraphs": [
        "You enter the village. It looks quite nice and is of a moderate size!",
        "You look back and the door is already shut closed.",
        "The village square is just before you."
      ],
      "actions": [
        {
          "text": "Go to Village Square",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "village_square"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "village_square",
      "name": "Village - Square",
      "paragraphs": [
        "The square is connected to most areas in the village.",
        "You see a building with a prominent sign: Tavern.",
        "By the edge of the square you find the quest board.",
        {
          "text": "Looks like the shopkeeper have open up for the day.",
          "showAny": [
            "opened_village_shop"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "From the shopkeepers instructions, you now see the way to the docks. The package feels heavy. Maybe you could give it to someone else?",
          "showAny": [
            "village_dock_opened"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "actions": [
        {
          "text": "Go to Tavern",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "village_tavern"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Go to Quest Board",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "village_square_quest_board",
              "chapterId": "chapter_3c_quest_board"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Go to Village Shop",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "village_shop_1",
              "chapterId": "chapter_3b_shop"
            }
          ],
          "showAny": [
            "opened_village_shop"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Make a visit to the town sheriff",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "village_sheriff"
            }
          ],
          "showAny": [
            "village_dock_opened"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Go to Village Docks",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "docks_1",
              "chapterId": "chapter_3d_docks"
            }
          ],
          "showAny": [
            "village_dock_opened"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Go to Mayor's manor",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "village_mayor_manor"
            }
          ],
          "showAny": [
            "village_sheriff_invited"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Go to Orchards by the High Roads",
          "showAny": [
            "opened_village_orchard"
          ],
          "triggers": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "village_tavern",
      "name": "Village - Tavern",
      "paragraphs": [
        "The first thing that strikes you is the noise. Fishermen know how to keep it lively.",
        "The tavern smells of good food and drinks - thankfully not too fishy.",
        {
          "text": "> You ask the barkeep about any quests. He recommend checking out the backside of the quest board for the... unusual quests.",
          "showAny": [
            "opened_village_quest_board_backside"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "> You ask the barkeep about shops for perusing any goods. He tips you about the village shop not far from the village square.",
          "showAny": [
            "opened_village_shop"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "actions": [
        {
          "text": "Ask barkeep about quests",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "add_flag",
              "target": "opened_village_quest_board_backside"
            }
          ],
          "hideAny": [
            "opened_village_quest_board_backside"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Ask barkeep about shops",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "add_flag",
              "target": "opened_village_shop"
            }
          ],
          "hideAny": [
            "opened_village_shop"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Back to Village Square",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "village_square"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "village_sheriff",
      "name": "Village - Sheriff",
      "paragraphs": [
        "Smoke fills your nostrils as you walk inside. A man in his 40s or 50s sits with his feet on a desk. The prominent star on his breast pocket sparkles.",
        "\"Now, what can I do for you?\"",
        {
          "text": "> You gave the package to the sheriff without explaining.",
          "showAny": [
            "village_sheriff_gave_package"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "\"Fella, I appreciate you giving me this package. But I need to know where you got this. If you don't, I will be forced to arrest you on the grounds of you carrying illicit goods.\"",
          "showAny": [
            "village_sheriff_gave_package"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "> You ratted out the shopkeeper and gave the sheriff the package.",
          "showAny": [
            "village_sheriff_gave_package_and_explained"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "\"Oh, mighty kind of you, sir... Or madam?\" He pauses. \"Anyway, now this mystery can finally be solved. Unfortunately I don't have a reward right now. But on behalf of the town mayor you're invited to dine at the mayor's manor later today. I'll make sure a fitting reward awaits you there.\" ",
          "showAny": [
            "village_sheriff_gave_package_and_explained"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "> You relented and ratted out the shopkeeper",
          "showAny": [
            "village_sheriff_gave_package_and_later_explained"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "\"Very wise of you.\" He pats you on the back. \"I understand you hesitatin', so I won't hold it against you. A dinner is being held at the major's manor later today. Consider yourself invited.\"",
          "showAny": [
            "village_sheriff_gave_package_and_later_explained"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "actions": [
        {
          "text": "Give him the package and explain everything",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "add_flag",
              "target": "village_sheriff_gave_package_and_explained"
            },
            {
              "type": "add_flag",
              "target": "village_sheriff_invited"
            }
          ],
          "hideAny": [
            "village_sheriff_gave_package_and_explained",
            "village_sheriff_gave_package"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Give him the package and explain nothing",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "add_flag",
              "target": "village_sheriff_gave_package"
            }
          ],
          "hideAny": [
            "village_sheriff_gave_package",
            "village_sheriff_gave_package_and_explained"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Relent and explain",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "add_flag",
              "target": "village_sheriff_gave_package_and_later_explained"
            },
            {
              "type": "add_flag",
              "target": "village_sheriff_invited"
            }
          ],
          "showAny": [
            "village_sheriff_gave_package"
          ],
          "hideAny": [
            "village_sheriff_gave_package_and_explained",
            "village_sheriff_gave_package_and_later_explained"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Refuse to explain",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "add_flag",
              "target": "village_sheriff_arrested"
            },
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "village_mayor_manor_dungeon"
            }
          ],
          "showAny": [
            "village_sheriff_gave_package"
          ],
          "hideAny": [
            "village_sheriff_gave_package_and_explained",
            "village_sheriff_gave_package_and_later_explained"
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Go back",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "village_square"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "village_mayor_manor",
      "name": "Village - Mayor's manor",
      "paragraphs": [
        "A dinner party!"
      ],
      "actions": [
        {
          "text": "Go back",
          "triggers": [
            {
              "type": "movement",
              "target": "village_square"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "village_mayor_manor_dungeon",
      "name": "Village - Mayor's manor - Dungeon",
      "paragraphs": [
        "You got arrested."
      ],
      "actions": [
        {
          "text": "Bang head against wall",
          "triggers": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
